-/* Gluster versions - OP-VERSION mapping
+/* RHS versions - OP-VERSION mapping
  *
- * 3.3.x                - 1
- * 3.4.x                - 2
- * 3.5.0                - 3
- * 3.5.1                - 30501
- * 3.6.0                - 30600
- * 3.7.0                - 30700
- * 3.7.1                - 30701
- * 3.7.2                - 30702
